summary: Marvel: “A lot of the deaths in Infinity War are permanent” Me, an intellectual: Sebastian Stan has a 9 movie contract, the...
body:
Marvel: “A lot of the deaths in Infinity War are permanent”

Me, an intellectual: Sebastian Stan has a 9 movie contract, the Spiderman sequel is filming with Tom Holland, Guardians of the Galaxy Vol III has been confirmed, a Black Panther sequel has been confirmed (not to mention it has a huge following), a Dr. Strange sequel has not been confirmed but is high likely, either Falcon or Bucky are likely to take on the mantle of Captain America… 

Seriously I could write a whole essay on this, who do they think they’re fooling?
